name: Nostalgi8RE
author: Anubi
description:
Revisited,
 Rebuilt, Reimagined. Nostalgi8RE is a built-from-the-ground-up remake 
of Nostalgi8, that aims at fixing some issues with the original version 
while adding it's own things to the mix (That I've learned in these two 
years making palettes). With more vibrant, desaturated colors, it's the 
perfect way to give a nostalgic feeling to your art.
